originalText.text: Dr Robin McKinney is the best doctor I've ever had. She takes great time to find holistic solutions for her patients' lives and offers concrete suggestions for wellness and lifestyle shifts. I would highly recommend her to anyone looking for a better connection in care.

originalText.text: Great staff. Very friendly. Wait time was not long. Dr. McKinney is a great doctor who cares about the well being of her patients. When my son was in the hospital I was able to speak to her about the next step of procedures we should have done. Love love love!

originalText.text: Dr. McKinney is a physician who cares about and treats the complete individual.  Her concern with what is effecting a life beyond the physical  allows her to create a summary diagnose from the root cause which leads to better health and healing.
